hole_4.original_tactic:
cases h₃ with
| inl h₃ =>
  have h₄ : i ∈ Multiset.replicate 659 3 := h₃
  have h₅ : i = 3 := by
    rw [Multiset.mem_replicate] at h₄
    exact h₄.2
  exact Or.inl h₅
| inr h₃ =>
  have h₄ : i ∈ ({ 2 } : Multiset ℕ) := h₃
  have h₅ : i = 2 := by simpa [Multiset.mem_singleton] using h₄
  exact Or.inr h₅
